{
  "id": "69b623649513fe18c0b5b986",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:心が疲れている時",
  "created": 1773544322,
  "updated": 1774042936,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b623649513fe18c0b5b986",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:心が疲れている時",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544322,
      "updated": 1773544322
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623820000000000a96d4d",
      "text": "放課後の教室。窓からやわらかい夕日が入っている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544322,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d4f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d50",
      "text": "ねえねえ、今日のテーマなんだけどさ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d51",
      "text": "「[心が疲れている時]」ってやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d52",
      "text": "いやマジでさ、テスト前とか、部活とか、SNSとかでメンタルHPゼロになる時あるじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d53",
      "text": "今日はそれをみんなでゆる〜く語ろうぜって回ね。よろ〜✌️",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d55",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d56",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d57",
      "text": "ええ、とてもよいテーマだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d58",
      "text": "心というものは、まるで湖の水のようなものですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d59",
      "text": "静かな時は澄んでおりますけれど、風が吹き続けますと、どうしても波立ってしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5a",
      "text": "疲れた心も、きっと同じなのだと思いますわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5d",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5e",
      "text": "心理学的には、いわゆる[** [精神的疲労]（mental fatigue）]の状態だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773577309
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d5f",
      "text": "簡単に言えば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d60",
      "text": " ストレスが長く続く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d61",
      "text": " 判断や集中をたくさん使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d62",
      "text": " 休息が不足する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d63",
      "text": "このあたりで、脳の処理リソースが消耗する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d64",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d65",
      "text": "https://www.apa.org/monitor/2018/07-08/mental-fatigue",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d66",
      "text": "要点をまとめると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d67",
      "text": "「心が弱いから疲れる」のではなく、脳のエネルギー問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d69",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6a",
      "text": "おおー、りかさん今日も理系オーラ出てるわ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6b",
      "text": "でもさ、それ聞くとちょっと安心じゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6c",
      "text": "なんか「自分メンタル弱すぎw」って思いがちだけど、ただの脳のバッテリー切れ説あるんだな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d6f",
      "text": "ええ、本当にそう思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d70",
      "text": "疲れているときに「自分がだめなのだ」と思ってしまう方も多いですけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d71",
      "text": "それはまるで、夜になって暗くなった空に向かって",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d72",
      "text": "「どうして昼のように明るくないの」と責めるようなものですものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d73",
      "text": "人の心にも、昼と夜があるのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d75",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d76",
      "text": "いい比喩だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d77",
      "text": "実際、脳の働きにも[回復サイクル]がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773577326
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d78",
      "text": "特に関係するのは、[前頭前野]。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1774042936
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d79",
      "text": "ここは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7a",
      "text": " 集中",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7b",
      "text": " 判断",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7c",
      "text": " 自制",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7d",
      "text": "などを担当している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7e",
      "text": "使いすぎるとパフォーマンスが落ちる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d7f",
      "text": "要するに――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d80",
      "text": "心が疲れる＝脳のコントロール装置の処理落ち。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d82",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d83",
      "text": "処理落ちって言い方めっちゃゲームっぽいw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d84",
      "text": "確かにさー、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d85",
      "text": "心が疲れてる時ってゲームもなんか楽しくない瞬間あるんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d86",
      "text": "普段なら神ゲーなのに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d87",
      "text": "「今日はもういいや…」ってなるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d89",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8a",
      "text": "ありますわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8b",
      "text": "私も、本を開いても、文字がすっと胸に入ってこない日がございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8c",
      "text": "まるで、言葉たちが窓の外で立ち止まっているようで。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8d",
      "text": "そんな日は、無理に読み進めず、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8e",
      "text": "ただ静かにお茶をいただくようにしています。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d90",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d91",
      "text": "それは合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d92",
      "text": "回復の方法としては、研究でもだいたいこの3つが言われている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d93",
      "text": "回復の基本",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d94",
      "text": " 1. [睡眠]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773577346
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d95",
      "text": " 2. [軽い運動]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773577352
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d96",
      "text": " 3. [心理的距離]（[気分転換]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773577361
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d97",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d98",
      "text": "https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6125016/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d99",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9a",
      "text": "「頑張って解決する」より「一度離れる」が有効。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9d",
      "text": "あーーそれわかる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9e",
      "text": "なんかさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96d9f",
      "text": "疲れてる時ほど[** 「もっと頑張らなきゃ」ってなる罠]あるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da0",
      "text": "完全にデバフ状態なのに無理にボス戦行くやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da3",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da4",
      "text": "ええ、本当に。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da5",
      "text": "疲れているときは、心が少し小さな声になりますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da6",
      "text": "「休みたい」と言っているのに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da7",
      "text": "私たちはつい、それを聞き逃してしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96da9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96daa",
      "text": "まとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dab",
      "text": "今日の要点",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dac",
      "text": "心の疲れは「性格」ではなく脳の疲労",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dad",
      "text": "無理に頑張ると悪化しやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dae",
      "text": "回復には休息・運動・気分転換",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96daf",
      "text": "つまり、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db0",
      "text": "システムにはメンテナンスが必要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db1",
      "text": "人間も例外ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db4",
      "text": "おおー今日めっちゃいい話じゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db5",
      "text": "結論これだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db6",
      "text": "心が疲れてる時は、サボりじゃなくてメンテ期間！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96db9",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dba",
      "text": "ええ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dbb",
      "text": "雨の日に花が休むように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dbc",
      "text": "人の心にも、そういう時間が必要なのだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dbd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dbe",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dbf",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc0",
      "text": "休息は怠慢ではなく、最適化。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc3",
      "text": "よし！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc4",
      "text": "ということで本日の鼎談まとめ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc5",
      "text": "「心が疲れたら、ちゃんと休もう。脳の充電だぞ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc6",
      "text": "みんなも無理すんなよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc7",
      "text": "HP回復しとこ！ 🎮✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623830000000000a96dc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544323,
      "updated": 1773544323
    },
    {
      "id": "69b623a70000000000a96dc9",
      "text": "#2026-03-15",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773544359,
      "updated": 1773544370
    },
    {
